metadata.name: MFA Gold Membership
metadata.description:
Get one of these NFTs to receive MFA Gold Membership:

-Exclusive gold-only sales with dedicated discounts on MFA third-party artist NFTs and on MFA own-created NFT series

-Free admittance, including priority pass, to all our physical gallery events in Rome, Italy, where Members will have the possibility to meet NFT artists, art collectors and experts, and establish network and collaborations

-Access to Discord, gold members-only sections and functionalities. For further details visit #membership channels on MFAâ€™s Discord official server (https://discord.gg/D9uCD2B8DW)

Note that all the services are subject to the Terms and Conditions as specified in our website.
